      • error_allowance_rate

        private double error_allowance_rate
        error allowance rate (Ɛ)

        Example:

        expected note: a

        error range: [a*2^(-Ɛ/12), a*2^(Ɛ/12)]

        a = 440Hz, Ɛ = 1 means error range: [G4#, A4#]
